NOTES:



IMAGiNE bringing you another release....The Chronicles of Narnia - The Voyage of the Dawn Treader



Right first the video source.....not a bad R5,but seen better.The video was a touch dull looking and lacked

some life and colour.also thought the colours were slightly off aswell.

Workdone.....well first thing was to filter the video so we made a script to crop,resize,sharpness,brightness,contrast

and chroma.Had to crop due to the thin black border and a weird thin blurry line across the top aswell .

Also then used a white balance and rgb filter.

Audio now for this we used the russian for the intro and end credits then we used our own line,but there was some issue

@ 12min mark so we needed to swap the audio for 30secs and then swap it back.



Overall a really nice R5 v9.5 a8.5 .......



Enjoy :)
